keepConnect.name: Nofo ma'u 'o fehokotaki
keepConnect.helperText: Kapau te ke lomiʻi ʻi he fehokotakiʻanga Kamata, pea tauhi ʻa e fehokotakiʻangá. 'Oku fie ma'u 'e he me'a ni 'a e tokanga 'e toe fehokotaki hokohoko 'a e fehokotaki'anga hili hono motuhi.

url.name: URL
url.helperText: Fakafehokotaki 'a e URL, hange ko 'eni ws://192.168.0.2:7001, pe wws://fakatātā/hala .
url.error: Ko e URL totonu ko e URL 'oku kamata 'aki 'a e ws:// pe wws://
